eventName: Racing Her Way to the Top

details.sectionContent: A guest lecture will be conducted by Ms. Mira Erda (The first Indian female Racer to compete in the Euro JK Series championship)

A seminar on women empowerment which will b conducted by Ms. Mira Erda. Encouragement will b given to all the participants present at the seminar. Her life journey will be presented to all. It will be an inspirational and motivational event for all the people present over there.
